{"tid":1198423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部稱所謂遊行人數證明民意的說法沒有很大說服力","createTime":"2019-06-10T08:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T08:38:56.000Z","uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29441c0a55f2b43f07713976032eeaae2143a685","tid":1198423,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人耿爽，回應有關香港昨日的反修例遊行時說，所謂的100萬人大遊行，香港特區政府已作出回應，特區政府公布的人數不是100萬，是少很多的數字，記者所謂的那個數字大、那個數字多，以證明誰代表民意，並沒有很大說服力。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽又說，目前有80多萬市民，參加撐修例大聯盟的活動，這是截至目前為止的數字，數字還會有增長，亦顯示主流民意支持修例。他說中央政府將繼續堅定支持特區政府，推進修訂條例的工作，堅決反對任何外部勢力，干預香港特區立法事務的錯誤言行。<br />\n<br />\n被問到所指的外部勢力是甚麼，耿爽說是一段時間以來，圍繞修例問題，一些國家發表的不負責任言論，又說外交部駐港特派員公署，已對此作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461912-20190610.htm?share=twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461912-20190610.htm%3Fshare%3Dtwitter&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=6f24b61b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461912-20190610.htm%3Fshare%3Dtwitter&h=56899360\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461912-20190610.htm?share=twitter</a>"},{"pid":"efafc93e12df25b9bdff08d46e8f7f5593048b51","tid":1198423,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:38:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I5ijUcOsciQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DI5ijUcOsciQ&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=865cf667\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I5ijUcOsciQ</a><br />\n<br />\n袁木記者會 (89.6.6) -- 六四事件"}]}